The Fall Detection Feature In This Smartwatch Is Designed To Enhance Safety By Automatically Detecting Potential Falls And Initiating Alerts. However, It May Not Be Foolproof, And False Alarms Or Missed Incidents Can Occur. This Feature Is Not A Substitute For Medical Or Professional Assistance. Users Should Not Solely Rely On It For Emergencies. Always Exercise Caution And Prioritize Personal Safety. The Accuracy And Functionality Of This Feature May Vary Depending On Factors Such As Sensor Calibration, User Behavior, And Environmental Conditions. We Recommend Maintaining Up-To-Date Contact Information And Informing Your Designated Emergency Contact About Their Role. Use This Feature As An Additional Layer Of Protection, But Remember To Seek Immediate Medical Attention Or Assistance From Relevant Authorities In Case Of An Emergency. By Using This Feature, You Acknowledge These Limitations And Agree To Use It Responsibly.

When Enabled, The Smartwatch Promptly Notifies You Upon Detecting A Fall. If You Cannot Acknowledge Or Dismiss The Alert Within A Set Timeframe, The Watch Initiates An Automatic Call To Your Pre-Defined Emergency Contact, Ensuring Swift Assistance During Critical Moments.
